Extract the summary information of the simpm object.

Source: R/summary.R
summary.simpm.Rd

summary.simpm summarizes and extracts the important information about the optimal PM design.

# S3 method for simpm
summary(object)

Arguments

object

The output object returned by simPM.

Value

The information about the optimal PM design.
